Attendez, les poissons !

00:06:50.010 --> 00:06:50.970
Regardez ça.

00:06:51.510 --> 00:06:52.380
Hein ?

00:06:58.810 --> 00:06:59.860
Je reconnais ça...

00:07:00.270 --> 00:07:01.860
Tu nous expliques ?

00:07:02.020 --> 00:07:04.940
